WEBVTT

00:17.840 --> 00:18.880
INTEGRITY, PRUDENCE, DILIGENCE

00:18.960 --> 00:20.120
Your Honor!

00:20.840 --> 00:22.200
Your Honor!

00:23.240 --> 00:24.360
Your Honor!

00:25.720 --> 00:29.440
You must grant justice to this poor woman!

00:32.720 --> 00:33.960
Your Honor!

00:35.160 --> 00:37.720
You must see justice done!

00:38.440 --> 00:40.320
You cursed girl!

00:40.400 --> 00:42.880
You even killed your own uncle!

00:45.640 --> 00:46.520
It's really him.

00:48.960 --> 00:50.560
Uncle…

00:51.440 --> 00:55.880
I beg you, Your Honor,
uphold justice for us.

01:00.240 --> 01:02.400
How… How did the plaintiff die?

01:03.000 --> 01:03.880
Your Honor,

01:03.960 --> 01:06.000
when I found Fan Daniu,
he had already died.

01:06.080 --> 01:07.400
There were multiple blade wounds.

01:07.480 --> 01:08.960
Long blade, by the look of it.

01:09.560 --> 01:12.040
Your Honor, in my view,

01:12.120 --> 01:14.320
the killer was skilled with the knife.

01:15.400 --> 01:16.600
It was her.

01:17.560 --> 01:19.080
If not her,

01:19.160 --> 01:22.120
who else would be so practiced
with a butcher's blade?

01:22.200 --> 01:24.840
I'll kill you! I'll kill you!

01:24.920 --> 01:26.880
Over a house? You'd murder for a house?

01:26.960 --> 01:29.240
Your Honor, I arrived
at the yamen at first light.

01:29.840 --> 01:31.640
The neighbors can testify!

01:31.720 --> 01:32.960
Yes, we can testify.

01:33.040 --> 01:33.880
We vouch for Changyu.

01:33.960 --> 01:36.600
-She was home last night.
-That's right.

01:36.680 --> 01:38.880
-We came here together this morning.
-Your Honor,

01:38.960 --> 01:40.840
-Changyu is innocent.
-Silence!

01:41.360 --> 01:43.160
I am still conducting this investigation.

01:44.200 --> 01:45.120
Your Honor,

01:45.200 --> 01:48.600
even if she did not
strike the blow herself,

01:48.680 --> 01:51.760
she could have hired someone.

01:51.840 --> 01:55.120
Why not search her house first?

01:55.840 --> 01:56.920
Yes, yes.

01:57.640 --> 01:58.760
Men!

01:58.840 --> 02:00.800
Detain Fan Changyu pending trial.

02:00.880 --> 02:02.840
-Yes, sir.
-I'll kill you! I'll kill you!

02:02.920 --> 02:03.680
-Changyu!
-Changyu!

02:03.760 --> 02:05.080
-It wasn't me!
-Changyu!

02:05.160 --> 02:06.160
Changyu!

02:06.800 --> 02:08.199
-Changyu!
-Changyu!

02:08.720 --> 02:10.280
Changyu, don't be afraid!

02:19.080 --> 02:21.280
‎She is innocent!

02:23.520 --> 02:24.840
Where is Constable Wang?

02:25.480 --> 02:28.800
Your Honor, he has already
taken men to the Fan residence.

02:41.160 --> 02:42.240
Search!

02:43.320 --> 02:44.440
Ning!

02:58.440 --> 02:59.960
My lord, no one upstairs.

03:00.560 --> 03:01.640
No one in the back courtyard.

03:01.720 --> 03:02.680
My lord, no one here.

03:05.000 --> 03:06.760
Someone came to the Fan house
seeking revenge.

03:07.280 --> 03:10.320
You two stay. The rest,
back to the yamen with me.

03:10.400 --> 03:11.440
-Yes.
-Yes.

04:39.000 --> 04:42.880
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

05:20.240 --> 05:21.280
Don't blow it.

05:21.360 --> 05:25.480
Changyu said if we meet bad people,
we blow the whistle.

05:26.280 --> 05:27.720
Not yet.

05:28.360 --> 05:29.800
If you blow it now,

05:30.720 --> 05:32.440
you'll only draw more of them.

05:51.360 --> 05:52.240
Mr. Wang.

05:53.720 --> 05:55.200
I didn't kill my uncle.

05:55.720 --> 05:56.680
I know.

05:57.600 --> 05:58.560
Changyu,

05:59.600 --> 06:00.880
something happened at your house too.

06:07.640 --> 06:09.040
When I arrived,

06:10.080 --> 06:11.640
there were three bodies on the ground.

06:15.920 --> 06:16.800
Where's Ning?

06:16.880 --> 06:18.120
Stay calm.

06:18.720 --> 06:21.280
Those bodies were not
your husband and Changning.

06:22.160 --> 06:23.160
The house was empty.

06:23.680 --> 06:25.600
But it had been turned upside down.

06:26.280 --> 06:28.800
Perhaps they only took them.

06:30.400 --> 06:32.760
There were reports of movement
in the hills outside the city.

06:32.840 --> 06:34.880
-The magistrate has sent men to search.
-I'll go find them.

06:34.960 --> 06:36.680
You cannot leave yet.

06:36.760 --> 06:39.120
-The magistrate has not released you.
-My parents are gone.

06:40.080 --> 06:42.600
My sister is all I have left, Mr. Wang.

06:42.680 --> 06:43.600
I'm begging you.

07:04.920 --> 07:05.920
Changyu.

07:07.240 --> 07:08.640
Be careful.

07:28.240 --> 07:29.120
Ning.

07:29.200 --> 07:30.640
Count to ten.

07:46.080 --> 07:47.080
Five.

07:47.600 --> 07:48.480
Six.

07:49.240 --> 07:50.480
Seven.

07:50.560 --> 07:51.680
Eight.

07:52.760 --> 07:53.800
Nine.

07:59.320 --> 08:00.320
Keep warm.

08:00.400 --> 08:03.400
As long as you're alive,
Changyu will come for you.

08:23.000 --> 08:24.560
Zheng.

08:25.200 --> 08:26.480
Zheng.

08:26.560 --> 08:28.160
Zheng.

08:29.520 --> 08:31.600
Turn around. Don't look.

10:01.360 --> 10:02.960
Let me go!

10:03.040 --> 10:05.000
Let me go!

10:08.000 --> 10:10.320
Let me go!

10:26.360 --> 10:27.600
I've killed someone.

10:33.080 --> 10:34.720
Changyu.

10:43.480 --> 10:44.560
Run.

10:45.840 --> 10:47.240
Don't worry about me.

10:47.920 --> 10:50.200
Take Changning and go!

10:54.920 --> 10:57.720
Changyu. Zheng.

11:01.920 --> 11:03.360
Good.

11:05.040 --> 11:07.800
Now that they're gone,
I can deal with you useless lot properly.

12:09.960 --> 12:10.880
How is it?

12:11.960 --> 12:13.440
I told you to leave.

12:13.520 --> 12:14.760
Why come back?

12:14.840 --> 12:17.520
I had to get Ning somewhere safe
before I could come back for you.

12:22.040 --> 12:23.000
Hold on.

12:23.840 --> 12:25.880
The constables will be here soon.
Just hold on!

13:13.880 --> 13:14.560
Stay focused.

13:20.800 --> 13:22.280
Who sent you?

13:22.360 --> 13:24.600
What did my family ever do
to deserve this?

13:46.000 --> 13:47.000
Yan Zheng!

13:48.240 --> 13:49.360
Yan Zheng!

13:58.440 --> 13:59.440
Stay awake.

14:00.200 --> 14:01.240
Don't fall asleep.

14:01.840 --> 14:02.840
We're almost home.

14:06.720 --> 14:07.880
This is the second time

14:08.440 --> 14:10.000
I've carried you out of the snow.

14:14.520 --> 14:17.560
Other women marry for someone
to hold up the household.

14:19.040 --> 14:20.080
Did I marry you

14:21.640 --> 14:23.440
just to build my strength?

14:27.200 --> 14:28.280
Don't fall asleep.

14:29.120 --> 14:29.960
Stay with me.

14:33.160 --> 14:34.400
You have to live.

14:34.480 --> 14:36.200
If anything happens to you,

14:36.280 --> 14:38.040
I could never repay what I owe.

14:42.480 --> 14:44.600
Get up. Don't fall asleep.

14:47.880 --> 14:49.480
Thank you for saving Ning.

14:51.240 --> 14:52.320
If she had died,

14:54.040 --> 14:57.280
I wouldn't know how to go on.

15:02.360 --> 15:03.360
You're my benefactor.

15:04.720 --> 15:06.000
Yan Zheng.

15:26.000 --> 15:26.920
Yan Zheng.

15:28.280 --> 15:29.120
Yan Zheng.

15:31.200 --> 15:32.240
Wake up.

15:33.560 --> 15:34.880
Don't fall asleep.

15:36.440 --> 15:38.840
Don't you dare sleep, Yan Zheng.

15:39.520 --> 15:40.560
Yan Zheng.

15:42.120 --> 15:43.080
Yan Zheng.

15:44.120 --> 15:45.120
Stay awake.

15:47.080 --> 15:48.160
Stay awake.

15:54.880 --> 15:57.040
Changyu!

16:10.280 --> 16:14.160
Changyu! Zheng, wake up!

16:14.240 --> 16:16.360
Changyu! Zheng!

16:16.440 --> 16:17.280
Let's go home.

16:17.360 --> 16:19.120
Changyu. Changyu!

16:20.320 --> 16:21.280
Changyu!

16:21.960 --> 16:22.800
Men!

16:38.040 --> 16:39.080
Zheng.

16:39.920 --> 16:42.800
Your father was a great man,
a hero of unshakable honor.

16:42.880 --> 16:45.880
One day,
you must grow into a man like him.

16:51.000 --> 16:53.160
Zheng, have more food.

16:53.240 --> 16:54.960
-Here, Father.
-Eat up.

16:55.040 --> 16:56.480
You need strength.

16:58.000 --> 16:59.240
Zheng, finish your meal.

16:59.320 --> 17:01.760
Grow up strong, just like Father.

17:06.200 --> 17:08.000
Xie Linshan.

17:08.920 --> 17:10.560
Xie Linshan.

17:12.599 --> 17:14.480
Xie Linshan…

17:15.040 --> 17:15.880
Mother.

17:26.760 --> 17:28.760
How could you break your word?

17:28.840 --> 17:32.240
You promised you'd come back
and paint my brows.

17:36.520 --> 17:37.720
Mother!

17:47.320 --> 17:50.000
WHERE CLOUDS MEET VERDURE

17:50.080 --> 17:51.160
Zheng.

17:51.680 --> 17:53.960
I made some osmanthus cakes for you.

17:54.040 --> 17:55.280
They're sweet.

17:55.360 --> 17:56.680
Go eat them outside.

17:56.760 --> 17:57.720
All right.

17:58.720 --> 18:02.360
When you come back, pick more blossoms.

18:02.440 --> 18:04.560
I will make more for you.

18:05.200 --> 18:07.840
Zheng, remember.

18:08.360 --> 18:11.360
I love osmanthus cake the most.

18:20.680 --> 18:22.360
No. Don't.

18:22.440 --> 18:24.240
Don't eat the osmanthus cake. Don't go!

18:31.800 --> 18:32.640
Mother.

18:35.920 --> 18:36.800
Mother!

18:37.680 --> 18:38.640
Mother!

18:39.240 --> 18:40.160
Mother!

18:44.240 --> 18:45.360
Mother…

19:19.800 --> 19:20.800
Mother.

19:40.680 --> 19:41.640
Zheng.

19:43.600 --> 19:45.120
Do not cling to me.

19:47.840 --> 19:49.960
I cannot stay and watch you grow.

20:10.880 --> 20:15.400
Mother, don't leave me.

20:30.440 --> 20:31.760
I was just giving you your medicine.

20:32.360 --> 20:33.920
You reacted like I was stabbing you.

20:37.040 --> 20:38.360
I'm sorry.

20:41.240 --> 20:43.040
-Here.
-I'll take it myself.

20:46.040 --> 20:49.640
Your hand has two deep sword cuts.

20:50.440 --> 20:52.000
And the web of your thumb is torn.

20:52.080 --> 20:55.440
The doctor said
you cannot strain either hand.

21:11.960 --> 21:14.360
It's fine. I don't like sweets.

21:14.440 --> 21:16.240
Don't worry. It's not osmanthus flavored.

21:17.440 --> 21:20.600
You kept shouting not to eat osmanthus.

21:22.120 --> 21:23.920
So I figured you didn't like it.

21:24.760 --> 21:25.680
It's candied tangerine peel.

21:29.320 --> 21:30.480
The doctor said your injuries

21:31.080 --> 21:32.720
are just as serious as last time.

21:33.560 --> 21:36.680
He kept telling me
you need to get proper rest.

21:37.680 --> 21:39.800
Until you've healed,

21:39.880 --> 21:41.640
you are not to lift anything heavy.

21:46.080 --> 21:49.440
Our house has been sealed by the yamen.
We can't return for now.

21:50.240 --> 21:51.880
We'll make do at Mr. Zhao's.

21:52.880 --> 21:54.560
You stay in the loft
and focus on recovering.

21:56.680 --> 21:59.440
Changyu. Yan Zheng. Supper's ready.

22:00.120 --> 22:01.360
All right.

22:03.920 --> 22:05.160
I'll go down first.

22:05.240 --> 22:06.600
I'll bring your meal up in a moment.

22:20.240 --> 22:21.720
Thank you for protecting Ning.

23:10.240 --> 23:11.360
Who sent you?

23:11.440 --> 23:13.480
What did my family ever do
to deserve this?

23:22.880 --> 23:24.440
Xuan Tie death warriors.

23:25.040 --> 23:27.240
The Weis' hounds have tracked us down.

23:28.840 --> 23:31.040
Yet they were not after me.

23:34.840 --> 23:36.040
XIGU ALLEY

23:36.120 --> 23:38.280
The air is dry.

23:38.960 --> 23:40.720
Beware of fire.

23:40.800 --> 23:42.360
Here. Take the brazier.

23:45.840 --> 23:47.560
You… are you cold?

23:47.640 --> 23:49.080
Why are your hands shaking like that?

23:49.160 --> 23:50.960
I… I don't know.

23:51.040 --> 23:53.240
Ever since we came back from the woods.

23:54.600 --> 23:55.440
That's…

23:55.520 --> 23:57.800
Probably just a chill. I'll be fine.

24:02.960 --> 24:04.040
Still up?

24:12.880 --> 24:14.400
Go back to sleep. I'll sit with you.

24:34.000 --> 24:36.280
When you woke at noon,
you were drenched in sweat.

24:37.720 --> 24:40.000
Was it because you killed someone?
A nightmare?

24:49.920 --> 24:50.800
Yes.

24:51.840 --> 24:53.560
It was my first time killing someone too.

24:55.680 --> 24:56.880
Are you afraid?

25:01.400 --> 25:02.360
Truth is,

25:04.840 --> 25:06.200
you're afraid as well.

25:10.360 --> 25:11.440
Not anymore.

25:14.280 --> 25:15.600
Just my hands won't stop shaking.

25:22.840 --> 25:24.520
You don't need to be afraid.

25:25.160 --> 25:27.240
Keep yourself busy these next few days.

25:27.320 --> 25:28.600
Slaughter a pig or two.

25:28.680 --> 25:30.240
Do you know how to butcher pigs?

25:30.320 --> 25:31.560
I'll teach you.

25:32.760 --> 25:33.760
This way,

25:34.520 --> 25:36.960
if you ever give up escorting caravans,
you'll still have a trade.

25:48.360 --> 25:49.240
Come sit here.

25:50.520 --> 25:51.560
It's warmer.

26:00.280 --> 26:01.120
They say

26:01.800 --> 26:04.280
butchers carry a killing aura.

26:04.360 --> 26:05.800
Even spirits won't come near.

26:06.600 --> 26:08.040
If I stay by you,

26:08.120 --> 26:09.640
you won't have nightmares.

26:20.360 --> 26:21.480
Thank you.

27:47.800 --> 27:49.960
Changning, fetch some water.

28:23.720 --> 28:24.920
Leave it there.

28:36.920 --> 28:39.800
Mr. Wang, has the magistrate
reached a verdict?

28:44.800 --> 28:46.280
-Constable Wang.
-Constable Wang.

28:52.960 --> 28:54.920
ARREST WARRANT

28:55.000 --> 28:55.840
By order of the magistrate,

28:56.880 --> 28:58.320
Fan family's son-in-law, Yan Zheng,

28:58.400 --> 28:59.880
is suspected of murder.

29:01.120 --> 29:02.840
He is to be taken into custody for trial.

29:08.440 --> 29:11.880
QINGPING COUNTY YAMEN

29:20.400 --> 29:22.720
INTEGRITY, PRUDENCE, DILIGENCE

29:32.720 --> 29:35.800
Fan Changyu, the case
of Fan Daniu remains unsettled.

29:35.880 --> 29:37.520
As a principal suspect,

29:37.600 --> 29:39.560
you should be confined awaiting trial.

29:40.320 --> 29:42.000
You fled in the confusion.

29:42.600 --> 29:45.400
I have yet to charge you for that.

29:45.480 --> 29:47.000
And now you deliver yourself back here?

29:47.640 --> 29:49.280
Men. Seize her as well.

29:50.480 --> 29:52.040
The head of my household has witnesses.

29:52.960 --> 29:54.400
She has nothing to do with the case.

29:55.000 --> 29:56.240
May I ask, Your Honor,

29:56.320 --> 29:58.760
in your investigation,
have you obtained any solid evidence?

30:02.800 --> 30:04.040
Fan family's live-in son-in-law,

30:04.800 --> 30:08.360
you married into the Fan household
without reporting it to the yamen.

30:09.240 --> 30:11.000
As a man from elsewhere,

30:11.080 --> 30:14.200
do you possess travel papers
to prove your identity?

30:14.280 --> 30:15.840
He does.

30:18.520 --> 30:19.600
Here.

30:19.680 --> 30:21.600
‎YAMEN

30:26.520 --> 30:28.160
REGISTRANT
FAN CHANGYU OF XIGU ALLEY, LIN'AN TOWN

30:29.880 --> 30:30.840
Just as I suspected.

30:33.040 --> 30:36.640
This travel pass was issued only recently.

30:36.720 --> 30:38.640
You have no original
registration documents.

30:38.720 --> 30:39.840
Correct?

30:39.920 --> 30:41.400
I encountered bandits on the road.

30:42.280 --> 30:43.280
My original papers were lost.

30:43.360 --> 30:44.440
TRAVEL PASS

30:44.520 --> 30:46.880
I've asked someone back home
to have them reissued.

30:47.400 --> 30:48.600
They will arrive soon.

30:50.480 --> 30:51.640
In other words,

30:52.520 --> 30:55.480
your documents are incomplete.

30:59.920 --> 31:00.760
Your Honor,

31:01.360 --> 31:02.600
Yan Zheng has married Fan Changyu.

31:02.680 --> 31:04.520
He now has a local guarantor.

31:04.600 --> 31:05.440
Under Dayin Code…

31:05.520 --> 31:06.960
Constable Wang. Silence.

31:13.320 --> 31:14.600
How dare you, base commoners!

31:15.160 --> 31:17.480
You dare pass yourselves off
as citizens of this county?

31:18.280 --> 31:21.720
I say you are bandits
from Qingfeng Stronghold!

31:22.960 --> 31:26.280
Working together to lure criminals here

31:26.360 --> 31:28.040
and ruin the peace of Lin'an!

31:28.960 --> 31:31.080
That is not true!
We are wronged, Your Honor!

31:31.160 --> 31:32.280
We are the victims!

31:32.360 --> 31:34.880
My sister and my husband
were nearly killed!

31:35.400 --> 31:37.240
How can you condemn us
without knowing the truth?

31:37.320 --> 31:38.320
Insolent!

31:38.400 --> 31:41.080
You dare accuse our magistrate?

31:41.160 --> 31:45.000
You claim you were nearly killed.

31:45.720 --> 31:47.800
Perhaps you quarreled over the loot

31:47.880 --> 31:49.840
and turned on each other.
That would not be unheard of.

32:01.120 --> 32:02.240
Give it a few more days.

32:02.320 --> 32:04.040
When the travel papers arrive,

32:04.120 --> 32:05.120
the truth will out.

32:07.720 --> 32:10.280
When I render judgment,
must I wait for you?

32:10.880 --> 32:12.120
Brazen vagrant.

32:12.200 --> 32:14.840
Full of lies and deceit!

32:14.920 --> 32:15.840
Guards!

32:15.920 --> 32:17.920
Twenty heavy strokes!

32:18.000 --> 32:20.600
Bring the confession
and have him press his mark!

32:21.200 --> 32:22.000
Stop!

32:22.920 --> 32:24.080
You serve the court.

32:24.760 --> 32:26.200
Will you beat a confession out of me?

32:26.880 --> 32:28.800
You dare slander this magistrate?

32:29.720 --> 32:31.480
Beat him! Harder!

32:31.560 --> 32:33.360
Your Honor, he is already wounded!

32:33.960 --> 32:35.720
If someone must be struck, strike me!

32:36.840 --> 32:38.880
Make him confess his ties to the bandits!

32:38.960 --> 32:39.880
Strike!

32:43.560 --> 32:44.600
Your Honor!

33:06.840 --> 33:07.800
Are you hurt?

33:10.280 --> 33:11.920
-I am fine.
-Outrageous!

33:12.000 --> 33:14.480
What do you think this courtroom is?

33:14.560 --> 33:15.440
Your Honor!

33:15.520 --> 33:17.160
Fan Changyu is innocent!

33:17.240 --> 33:19.160
Have mercy on these poor souls
who lost their parents!

33:19.240 --> 33:20.080
Yes!

33:20.160 --> 33:21.160
Have mercy!

33:22.600 --> 33:23.960
-Wearing your official hat…
-Let them go!

33:24.040 --> 33:25.200
-…to bully an orphan?
-That's right! You can't bully her!

33:25.280 --> 33:26.720
-What justice is this?
-How can you treat people this way?

33:28.280 --> 33:29.800
They are wronged, Your Honor!

33:29.880 --> 33:31.000
They are wronged!

33:31.600 --> 33:33.960
Please, Your Honor!

33:34.040 --> 33:35.040
Your Honor.

33:35.120 --> 33:36.520
Why not wait a few more days,

33:36.600 --> 33:37.920
lest an injustice be done?

33:39.600 --> 33:41.840
Your Honor, public opinion carries weight.

33:41.920 --> 33:43.360
You do not wish to stir their anger.

33:44.680 --> 33:46.000
‎Your Honor…

33:46.080 --> 33:47.400
Silence!

33:48.640 --> 33:50.080
One case at a time.

33:50.800 --> 33:53.720
Fan Changyu,
as a suspect in the Fan Daniu case,

33:53.800 --> 33:55.160
you should not even be here.

33:56.600 --> 33:58.760
Constable Wang, take her back to the jail.

34:02.000 --> 34:03.200
Yes.

34:07.600 --> 34:09.760
Changyu, come with me.

34:14.480 --> 34:15.400
It is all right.

34:56.880 --> 34:59.840
Your Honor, lock her up.
That's the safest place.

35:00.360 --> 35:03.400
In the end, the body
will be all the proof you need.

35:10.120 --> 35:13.000
-I will give you one last--
-I will give you one final chance.

35:23.800 --> 35:25.800
Outrageous. Seize him!

35:38.480 --> 35:39.880
I speak of the law,

35:40.640 --> 35:42.200
yet you insist on framing me.

35:43.680 --> 35:44.840
Very well.

35:46.200 --> 35:47.680
Then we shall follow my rules.

35:47.760 --> 35:49.360
You… What are you doing?

35:50.080 --> 35:51.840
You are a mere commoner!

35:51.920 --> 35:54.960
Do you dare harm our magistrate?

35:55.040 --> 35:57.440
A mere county magistrate.

35:58.880 --> 36:00.560
Do you dare speak of rebellion?

36:00.640 --> 36:01.480
You…

36:01.560 --> 36:02.640
What are you saying?

36:02.720 --> 36:04.280
It is you who oversteps your authority.

36:04.800 --> 36:07.280
Gentleman, do not be rash.

36:20.320 --> 36:21.360
Yan Zheng!

36:32.680 --> 36:33.720
Your Honor,

36:34.240 --> 36:36.080
are you not taking this rather too far?

36:36.160 --> 36:37.480
YAN ZHENG

36:37.560 --> 36:38.920
Yan Zheng's travel papers are here.

36:44.400 --> 36:45.520
Internal injury?

36:52.080 --> 36:53.000
Did you miss me?

36:53.080 --> 36:54.560
Starting to appreciate me now?

36:54.640 --> 36:55.760
If you had come any later,

36:56.400 --> 36:57.880
I would have smashed this place apart.

36:57.960 --> 36:59.840
Better to avoid further trouble.
Leave it to me.

37:01.840 --> 37:03.200
Your Honor,

37:03.280 --> 37:05.440
Yan Zheng is a student of Luyuan Academy.

37:05.520 --> 37:07.320
His travel documents
and credentials are all here.

37:07.400 --> 37:08.960
Might we speak privately?

37:10.600 --> 37:11.920
Luyuan Academy?

37:13.440 --> 37:14.440
Please.

37:14.520 --> 37:17.680
YAMEN

37:21.080 --> 37:25.240
INTEGRITY, PRUDENCE, DILIGENCE

37:27.400 --> 37:28.400
Please.

37:28.480 --> 37:30.240
JUSTICE IS BLIND

37:34.480 --> 37:35.840
It is settled. Rest easy.

37:35.920 --> 37:38.200
Your Honor, he is only a scholar.

37:38.280 --> 37:39.600
Was such courtesy necessary?

37:39.680 --> 37:40.520
What do you know?

37:40.600 --> 37:43.160
Luyuan Academy stands at the pinnacle
of scholarship in this realm.

37:43.240 --> 37:46.600
Those noble heirs
aren't people I can afford to offend.

37:46.680 --> 37:48.680
Neither of us can reveal who we truly are.

37:48.760 --> 37:49.800
Better to avoid more trouble.

37:50.400 --> 37:52.160
He is unfit to hold office.

37:53.200 --> 37:54.920
A yard fowl strutting among tiles.

37:55.000 --> 37:57.480
Deal with him however you like later.
Right now, we're on their turf.

37:57.560 --> 37:58.440
Let's get out first.

38:11.080 --> 38:13.160
I have reviewed the facts.

38:13.240 --> 38:15.640
Hear the verdict.

38:17.760 --> 38:21.040
Summon Madam Mi, widow of Fan Daniu.

38:28.360 --> 38:31.760
Yan Zheng is a lawful citizen.

38:31.840 --> 38:35.960
In defending his family,
he was forced to kill a bandit.

38:36.600 --> 38:38.760
He has no ties to Qingfeng Stronghold.

38:38.840 --> 38:41.680
He is therefore acquitted.

38:42.680 --> 38:44.560
-Wonderful!
-And Fan Changyu?

38:44.640 --> 38:46.680
Yes, what about Fan Changyu?

38:47.880 --> 38:52.280
At present, there is no evidence
that Fan Changyu is the true culprit.

38:52.360 --> 38:54.280
She is to be released as well.

38:56.400 --> 38:58.800
Your Honor!

38:58.880 --> 39:01.320
You must grant this widow justice!

39:02.080 --> 39:04.280
Fan Daniu died unjustly!

39:04.960 --> 39:05.800
Silence!

39:06.960 --> 39:09.440
It is because of you,
you quarrelsome shrew!

39:09.520 --> 39:10.600
Shouting and wailing in court.

39:10.680 --> 39:11.920
Have you no decorum?

39:12.000 --> 39:14.520
Right and wrong are for me to determine.

39:14.600 --> 39:16.520
If any of you continue this disturbance,

39:16.600 --> 39:17.800
you will be punished severely.

39:20.400 --> 39:21.480
Court dismissed.

39:25.880 --> 39:27.480
-Careful.
-All right, disperse!

39:27.560 --> 39:29.080
-Yan Zheng!
-Yan Zheng!

39:33.520 --> 39:34.920
Good thing I arrived when I did.

39:35.000 --> 39:36.560
Another second and you'd be dead.

39:40.120 --> 39:42.240
Yan Zheng. Yan Zheng.

39:44.360 --> 39:46.200
Take care of Fan Changyu.

39:46.280 --> 39:47.560
Of course.

39:50.520 --> 39:51.600
Yan Zheng!

39:51.680 --> 39:52.800
Who is Fan Changyu?

42:30.840 --> 42:34.520
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS FILM

42:34.600 --> 42:35.440
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
